♪Your smiling face, slowly fading away♪

201
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:27,210
♪I can't forget♪

202
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:31,420
♪That arched bridge, curving gracefully♪

203
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:34,990
♪My window, permeated
with thoughts of you♪

204
00:12:34,990 --> 00:12:36,700
♪This hometown♪

205
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:41,050
♪Where only moonlight still
sways and dances in the night♪

206
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:44,300
♪I've walked through ten miles
of crabapples♪

207
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:46,090
♪Watching the wind turn them gold♪

208
00:12:46,090 --> 00:12:48,670
♪The verdant grass withers,
and the setting sun defeated♪

209
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:51,600
♪Waiting for you is my arrogance♪

210
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:55,260
♪Counting the endless roads
that stretch to the horizon's edge♪

211
00:12:55,640 --> 00:12:58,200
♪I turn back
from ten miles of crabapples♪

212
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:00,200
♪A tale of sorrow♪

213
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,780
♪The west wind blows,
but no wild goose returns♪

